{
  "texts": [
    "We defer detailed descriptions of TacticAI's components to the \"Methods\" section.",
    "Note that, all our error bars reported in this research are standard deviations.",
    "We evaluate the three components of TacticAI on a relevant benchmark dataset of corner kicks.",
    "Our dataset consists of 7176 corner kicks from the 2020 to 2021 Premier League seasons, which we randomly shuffle and split into a training (80%) and a test set (20%).",
    "As previously mentioned, TacticAI operates on graphs."
  ]
}